          <li class="green-para">• In case of a refund on 30-Day Money Back, payment of the refund amount shall be done via online bank transfer to the customer's bank account within 10 days of receipt of the product. If the mode of the payment was through online debit / credit card / net banking, the refund will be processed by reversal of the transaction.</li>
          <li class="green-para">• In case the exchange value is higher than the value of the old product, the customer will have to pay the difference.</li>
          <li class="green-para">• In case the exchanged value is lesser than the value of the old product, the difference will be refunded in case of a 30-Day exchange, but if it’s a Lifetime Exchange then the difference will be held as a credit for future purchase.</li>
